>

<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/receiver/data/v1/funds/investments/transactions-current/{consentPactualId}/{investmentId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Endpoint that our client must call to get the information from Open Finance:
    
* Open Finance endpoint that will be requested: ```(GET /investments/{investmentId}/transactions-current)```
    
* FamilyType: ```Investimentos - Fundos de Investimento``` 
    
The response content provided by this endpoint uses the same entity as the provided on the [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/184058368/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DC+Fundos+de+Investimento+-+v1.0.2).
